1
00:00:23,840 --> 00:00:25,800
These are the test papers for this exam.

2
00:00:25,800 --> 00:00:27,080
Before you start answering,

3
00:00:27,080 --> 00:00:30,760
write your name, student ID, and class on the paper.

4
00:00:30,760 --> 00:00:32,960
The exam time is 90 minutes.

5
00:00:33,080 --> 00:00:34,920
Everyone must follow the exam rules.

6
00:00:34,920 --> 00:00:36,520
Don't whisper to each other.

7
00:00:38,440 --> 00:00:40,480
I, Yin Zixi,

8
00:00:40,760 --> 00:00:42,280
have a 20-year-old appearance,

9
00:00:42,280 --> 00:00:43,560
a 30-year-old soul,

10
00:00:43,840 --> 00:00:45,480
am an uploader in the media section,

11
00:00:45,480 --> 00:00:47,140
and have 3 million followers.

12
00:00:47,480 --> 00:00:50,940
The overachiever who insists on doing a live stream every day.

13
00:00:50,960 --> 00:00:52,640
It should be A.

14
00:00:56,120 --> 00:00:57,520
But now I realize

15
00:00:57,520 --> 00:00:59,400
that all these years were for nothing.

16
00:00:59,400 --> 00:01:01,000
Now, every time I solve a question,

17
00:01:01,000 --> 00:01:03,480
it costs me 108,600 brain cells

18
00:01:03,480 --> 00:01:05,209
to awaken my distant memories.

19
00:01:05,720 --> 00:01:08,780
If three are long and one is short, choose the shortest.

20
00:01:24,880 --> 00:01:26,560
Stop writing and hand in your papers.

21
00:01:26,560 --> 00:01:28,960
Phew, finally done.

22
00:01:33,240 --> 00:01:35,170
There's still another test paper.

23
00:01:40,759 --> 00:01:42,600
If two are long and two are short, choose B.

24
00:01:42,600 --> 00:01:44,080
If they are uneven, choose C.

25
00:01:44,080 --> 00:01:46,610
Copy and guess, and you will definitely pass.

26
00:01:50,640 --> 00:01:51,479
Senior,

27
00:01:51,479 --> 00:01:53,960
isn't there still 10 minutes left before the exam ends?

28
00:01:53,960 --> 00:01:55,280
I am the proctor.

29
00:01:55,280 --> 00:01:56,960
When I say hand it in, you hand it in.

30
00:01:56,960 --> 00:01:58,520
This is unfair to our class.

31
00:01:58,520 --> 00:02:00,680
Why are you students so difficult?

32
00:02:00,680 --> 00:02:02,120
You never study hard.

33
00:02:02,240 --> 00:02:05,500
Even with twenty extra minutes, it still wouldn't be done.

34
00:02:05,680 --> 00:02:06,800
Senior.

35
00:02:06,800 --> 00:02:08,280
Just talk.

36
00:02:08,280 --> 00:02:09,539
Don't point at others.

37
00:02:16,560 --> 00:02:17,680
I'm sorry.

38
00:02:28,000 --> 00:02:28,760
Everything

39
00:02:29,320 --> 00:02:31,160
started when I found this diary.

40
00:02:31,240 --> 00:02:33,570
That's all for the process improvements.

41
00:02:33,640 --> 00:02:36,320
I know everyone hates meetings.

42
00:02:36,320 --> 00:02:37,520
Now,

43
00:02:37,520 --> 00:02:39,120
let's move on to the final topic.

44
00:02:39,120 --> 00:02:40,360
Damn, it's almost time to get off work.

45
00:02:40,360 --> 00:02:41,480
And he's still dragging us into a meeting.

46
00:02:41,480 --> 00:02:42,400
Recently, we've been trying

47
00:02:42,400 --> 00:02:43,840
to integrate trending news into our livestreams.

48
00:02:43,840 --> 00:02:46,000
This is the real me, Yin Zixi.

49
00:02:46,520 --> 00:02:48,160
A miserable corporate slave.

50
00:02:48,160 --> 00:02:50,000
Although I have three million followers,

51
00:02:50,000 --> 00:02:51,760
the account belongs to the company.

52
00:02:51,760 --> 00:02:53,320
Especially Yin Zixi's

53
00:02:53,320 --> 00:02:55,480
report on the Cloud Data Center.

54
00:02:55,840 --> 00:02:57,800
It reached number 1 on the trending list.

55
00:02:57,800 --> 00:02:59,120
Everyone should take it as a reference.

56
00:02:59,120 --> 00:03:00,880
It actually made the headlines.

57
00:03:00,880 --> 00:03:02,480
What's going on?

58
00:03:09,000 --> 00:03:11,720
Do you all find it a bit strange?

59
00:03:11,720 --> 00:03:12,640
Actually,

60
00:03:12,640 --> 00:03:14,280
it's not strange at all.

61
00:03:14,280 --> 00:03:17,320
Because I provided this news report.

62
00:03:17,600 --> 00:03:19,440
Yin Zixi getting on the trending list

63
00:03:19,440 --> 00:03:21,100
was all thanks to my guidance.

64
00:03:21,320 --> 00:03:24,040
Don't think that just because I'm not on the frontlines,

65
00:03:24,040 --> 00:03:25,000
I don't know things.

66
00:03:25,000 --> 00:03:27,160
I have a keen sense for hot topics.

67
00:03:27,160 --> 00:03:28,160
This kind of news,

68
00:03:28,160 --> 00:03:29,520
most people would find worthless.

69
00:03:29,520 --> 00:03:30,240
Sorry.

70
00:03:30,240 --> 00:03:31,640
I need to take this call.

71
00:03:32,880 --> 00:03:34,079
Hurry back.

72
00:03:34,760 --> 00:03:36,920
Everyone, take a close look.

73
00:03:39,280 --> 00:03:40,760
Uncle He, what's wrong?

74
00:03:40,760 --> 00:03:41,600
Zixi,

75
00:03:41,600 --> 00:03:43,880
the report that got you trending is fake.

76
00:03:44,040 --> 00:03:45,040
Fake?

77
00:03:45,040 --> 00:03:46,200
This is a frame-up.

78
00:03:46,320 --> 00:03:48,240
The report doesn't match the facts.

79
00:03:48,240 --> 00:03:50,320
They only gave the news to your company.

80
00:03:50,320 --> 00:03:52,320
I suspect someone is targeting you.

81
00:03:52,680 --> 00:03:54,280
Tell your manager to come out.

82
00:03:54,280 --> 00:03:55,280
You made us trend online.

83
00:03:55,280 --> 00:03:57,920
You must give me an explanation today.

84
00:03:58,600 --> 00:03:59,660
What's that sound?

85
00:03:59,840 --> 00:04:01,040
Hello?

86
00:04:01,920 --> 00:04:03,560
Yin Zixi.

87
00:04:03,560 --> 00:04:04,400
Long time no see.

88
00:04:04,400 --> 00:04:05,600
Do we know each other?

89
00:04:05,720 --> 00:04:07,440
You have a short memory,

90
00:04:07,440 --> 00:04:08,720
big streamer.

91
00:04:09,320 --> 00:04:11,080
What can I do for you?

92
00:04:12,680 --> 00:04:15,240
You wrote this report, didn't you?

93
00:04:16,600 --> 00:04:18,360
Xihai City Cloud Data Center.

94
00:04:18,360 --> 00:04:20,880
It really is about this report.

95
00:04:21,320 --> 00:04:24,040
I did broadcast this news.

96
00:04:25,440 --> 00:04:27,160
Who are you?

97
00:04:28,840 --> 00:04:31,120
Do you know how much loss

98
00:04:31,120 --> 00:04:32,980
this report brought to my client?

99
00:04:33,320 --> 00:04:34,159
Miss Wen,

100
00:04:34,680 --> 00:04:37,040
we can talk this over.

101
00:04:37,720 --> 00:04:38,920
Yin Zixi,

102
00:04:39,120 --> 00:04:41,240
don't you check the materials before reporting?

103
00:04:41,240 --> 00:04:43,080
The news of Xihai University back then,

104
00:04:43,080 --> 00:04:44,440
wasn't it live-streamed by you?

105
00:04:44,440 --> 00:04:45,240
Me?

106
00:04:45,440 --> 00:04:47,520
What you did at Xihai University,

107
00:04:47,520 --> 00:04:49,680
I will never forget for the rest of my life.

108
00:04:49,680 --> 00:04:51,680
I didn't know you in college.

109
00:04:52,159 --> 00:04:53,760
Since you dared to report it,

110
00:04:53,880 --> 00:04:55,960
you must be prepared.

111
00:04:58,400 --> 00:05:00,040
This is my lawyer's letter.

112
00:05:01,320 --> 00:05:02,650
I'll be waiting for you.

113
00:05:08,240 --> 00:05:09,760
Two million.

114
00:05:12,880 --> 00:05:13,680
Yin Zixi,

115
00:05:13,680 --> 00:05:15,760
Didn't you check this report material even once?

116
00:05:15,760 --> 00:05:16,840
Even though I gave you the lead

117
00:05:16,840 --> 00:05:17,840
and the material,

118
00:05:17,840 --> 00:05:19,160
you still should have checked it.

119
00:05:19,160 --> 00:05:20,440
Otherwise, what do I need you for?

120
00:05:20,440 --> 00:05:21,840
Even though I said to catch the trend...

121
00:05:21,840 --> 00:05:23,240
You've said it all.

122
00:05:23,400 --> 00:05:25,200
You were the one who said there was no time to check.

123
00:05:25,200 --> 00:05:27,000
I might as well stream it myself.

124
00:05:29,360 --> 00:05:30,720
This Wen Lingli

125
00:05:30,960 --> 00:05:32,240
seems to know you.

126
00:05:32,920 --> 00:05:35,159
Why don't you go plead with her

127
00:05:35,159 --> 00:05:37,240
and ask her not to sue us?

128
00:05:37,560 --> 00:05:39,480
Otherwise, get out of here.

129
00:05:39,480 --> 00:05:41,000
Your operating account has nothing to do with our company.

130
00:05:41,000 --> 00:05:42,400
You handle this compensation yourself.

131
00:05:42,400 --> 00:05:43,720
Don't drag us down with you,

132
00:05:43,720 --> 00:05:45,080
big streamer.

133
00:05:46,120 --> 00:05:47,640
Wh-What are you doing?

134
00:05:47,640 --> 00:05:48,680
What am I doing?

135
00:05:48,680 --> 00:05:50,409
I'm hitting a scumbag like you.

136
00:05:58,280 --> 00:05:59,000
Yin Zixi!

137
00:05:59,320 --> 00:06:00,000
Yin Zixi!

138
00:06:00,120 --> 00:06:01,480
What are you waiting for?

139
00:06:01,480 --> 00:06:03,040
I will solve this myself.

140
00:06:03,040 --> 00:06:04,400
The account that belongs to me,

141
00:06:04,400 --> 00:06:06,000
I will get it back myself.

142
00:06:14,880 --> 00:06:18,240
Do you know why Wen Lingli is targeting you?

143
00:06:18,880 --> 00:06:21,080
Why is she targeting me?

144
00:06:21,920 --> 00:06:25,480
Xihai University news.

145
00:06:40,640 --> 00:06:43,159
I've almost gone through all the news about this university.

146
00:06:43,159 --> 00:06:45,760
I can't remember anything.

147
00:06:45,760 --> 00:06:47,360
I'm doomed now.

148
00:06:55,920 --> 00:07:00,380
A washed-up streamer is ruthlessly framed after offending a big conglomerate.

149
00:07:01,120 --> 00:07:03,840
After going bankrupt, no one dares to hire her.

150
00:07:04,360 --> 00:07:07,080
From then on, she begins a life of wandering.

151
00:07:08,760 --> 00:07:11,440
Wow, what a great harvest.

152
00:07:12,000 --> 00:07:13,120
Hmm, no, no.

153
00:07:13,120 --> 00:07:13,920
Wake up.

154
00:07:13,920 --> 00:07:15,320
Yin Zixi, wake up.

155
00:07:17,120 --> 00:07:19,320
What on earth am I thinking about?

156
00:07:19,600 --> 00:07:21,560
Is anyone there?

157
00:07:21,560 --> 00:07:22,960
Help!

158
00:07:22,960 --> 00:07:23,880
Can anyone help me?

159
00:07:23,880 --> 00:07:25,360
Granny, I'm coming.

160
00:07:31,840 --> 00:07:34,080
Granny, are you alright?

161
00:07:34,480 --> 00:07:35,360
I...

162
00:07:35,680 --> 00:07:36,800
I'm fine.

163
00:07:37,000 --> 00:07:37,680
Okay.

164
00:07:39,240 --> 00:07:40,800
Hey, miss.

165
00:07:41,040 --> 00:07:44,720
Why do you look so familiar to me?

166
00:07:45,200 --> 00:07:45,960
Do I?

167
00:07:45,960 --> 00:07:46,560
Oh.

168
00:07:46,840 --> 00:07:48,280
I remember now.

169
00:07:48,560 --> 00:07:50,000
I saw you in that

170
00:07:50,720 --> 00:07:52,600
trash.

171
00:07:52,600 --> 00:07:54,200
Me? Trash?

172
00:07:54,200 --> 00:07:54,800
Yeah.

173
00:07:55,280 --> 00:07:56,360
Wait here.

174
00:08:01,560 --> 00:08:02,440
Look.

175
00:08:03,560 --> 00:08:04,880
It's you, right?

176
00:08:05,160 --> 00:08:06,760
This is me.

177
00:08:06,760 --> 00:08:09,240
Why don't I remember this at all?

178
00:08:16,440 --> 00:08:17,440
Ah!

179
00:08:22,040 --> 00:08:26,240
Ah!

180
00:08:27,120 --> 00:08:28,640
What are you yelling for?

181
00:08:28,640 --> 00:08:31,160
Don't you know people have classes during the day?

182
00:08:31,160 --> 00:08:32,679
Are you crazy?

183
00:08:32,679 --> 00:08:33,679
You're already in college.

184
00:08:33,679 --> 00:08:35,559
Why are you still wearing a school uniform?

185
00:08:35,559 --> 00:08:36,960
Sorry.

186
00:08:38,280 --> 00:08:40,120
Isn't that Wen Lingli?

187
00:08:40,120 --> 00:08:42,520
Why does she seem a bit different?

188
00:08:42,799 --> 00:08:44,000
Excuse me.

189
00:08:44,360 --> 00:08:46,120
You saw the activity

190
00:08:46,120 --> 00:08:47,680
on this banner, right?

191
00:08:48,360 --> 00:08:51,560
Xihai University 2016.

192
00:08:57,880 --> 00:08:58,720
Ah.

193
00:08:59,000 --> 00:09:01,760
October 10, 2016.

194
00:09:02,120 --> 00:09:03,360
I time-traveled!

195
00:09:07,120 --> 00:09:08,320
Diary.

196
00:09:09,720 --> 00:09:12,840
Today I saw Wen Lingli bullying a classmate.

197
00:09:12,840 --> 00:09:14,080
I really couldn't stand it.

198
00:09:14,080 --> 00:09:15,360
I stepped forward to stop her.

199
00:09:15,360 --> 00:09:17,640
For this endorsement activity,

200
00:09:17,960 --> 00:09:20,840
can you not participate?

201
00:09:29,560 --> 00:09:31,720
Stop! Let go of that girl.

202
00:09:41,000 --> 00:09:42,960
I've tolerated you for a long time.

203
00:09:42,960 --> 00:09:44,880
Making such a fuss here.

204
00:09:44,880 --> 00:09:46,600
Since you've already let her go,

205
00:09:46,600 --> 00:09:48,040
I'll be leaving now.

206
00:09:58,960 --> 00:10:00,840
Assistant Casting Director Xi Chongjing

207
00:10:00,840 --> 00:10:02,760
Props Assistant Li Kunxiao

208
00:10:02,760 --> 00:10:04,680
Grip Truck Yi Mingle

209
00:10:04,720 --> 00:10:06,640
Yitong
